---
/**
 * Contribuer - PC800.fr
 * Section factuelle, sans claims inventés
 */
---

<section id="contribuer" class="section bg-metal-900">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <span class="section-header__label text-red-400">Participer</span>
      <h2 class="section-header__title text-white mx-auto">Contribuer au site</h2>
      <p class="section-header__intro text-gray-400 mx-auto">
        Ce site grandit grâce aux passionnés. Vous pouvez aider simplement : corriger une info, proposer une photo, ou suggérer un sujet d'article.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Actions -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Proposer une photo -->
      <div class="bg-metal-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-metal-700 hover:border-metal-600 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-700/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Proposer une photo</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
          Vous avez une PC800, une restauration, un accessoire rare ? Envoyez une photo (avec l'année et le modèle si possible).
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@pc800.fr?subject=Photo%20PC800" class="inline-flex items-center text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
          Envoyer une photo
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Suggérer un article -->
      <div class="bg-metal-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-metal-700 hover:border-metal-600 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-700/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Suggérer un article</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
          Un guide que vous auriez aimé trouver ? Une panne fréquente ? Une astuce touring ? Dites-moi.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@pc800.fr?subject=Suggestion%20article" class="inline-flex items-center text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
          Suggérer un sujet
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Signaler une correction -->
      <div class="bg-metal-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-metal-700 hover:border-metal-600 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-700/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Signaler une correction</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">
          Une spec, une valeur, une date, une coquille : chaque détail compte pour la qualité du site.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@pc800.fr?subject=Correction" class="inline-flex items-center text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
          Signaler
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact / Newsletter -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-metal-800">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Restez informé</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          Suivez l'actualité du site. Pas de spam, juste les nouveaux articles et outils.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Merci ! Vous serez informé des nouveautés.');">
        <input 
          type="email" 
          placeholder="votre@email.com"
          class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-metal-800 border border-metal-700 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-red-500"
          required
        />
        <button 
          type="submit"
          class="px-6 py-3 bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-800 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          S'inscrire
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .section { padding: 6rem 0; } }
  
  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .section-header__label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .section-header__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-header__intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .bg-metal-900 { background-color: #1C1917; }
  .bg-metal-800 { background-color: #292524; }
  .border-metal-700 { border-color: #44403C; }
  .border-metal-600 { border-color: #57534E; }
  .text-red-400 { color: #F87171; }
  .text-red-300 { color: #FCA5A5; }
  .text-red-500 { color: #EF4444; }
</style>